# 本目录文档关系图
# 源: roadmap.md §8

direction: right

M: "methodology.md\n评分口径"
CS: "current-state.md\nHEAD 速览"
A: "architecture-issues.md\n10 ARCH-*"
F: "functional-gaps.md\n12 FUNC-*"
FA: "failure-modes.md\n11 FAIL-*"
P: "performance-concerns.md\n10 PERF-*"
O: "observability-gaps.md\n12 OBS-*"
S: "security-concerns.md\n15 SEC-*"
I: "improvements.md\n主题级 fix"
R: "roadmap.md\n本文" { style.fill: "#dfd" }

M -> A
M -> F
M -> FA
M -> P
M -> O
M -> S
CS -> A
CS -> F
CS -> FA
CS -> P
CS -> O
CS -> S

